source.name: International Energy Outlook Table Browser
source.description: The International Energy Outlook 2011 presents EIA's long-term assessment of world energy markets. The International Energy Outlook 2011 (IEO2011) includes projections of world energy demand by region and primary energy source through 2035; electricity generation by fuel type; and energy-related carbon dioxide emissions.
